	DomainUI: {
		// TitleText: Ocean Domain
		// ExtraEyeTitleText: 10th Layer
		// CrashedLabelText: SYSTEM CRASH
		/* EyeDesc1:
			'''
			The first eye opens, tearing a rift in the dark side of your consciousness.
			You hear the sound of tides that should not exist, and a damp chill begins to seep into the veil of reality.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc2:
			'''
			The second eye overlaps with the first; your vision blurs with unfocusable double images.
			The real world blurs like a water-soaked photograph, while a grey ocean from another dimension forcibly overwrites the current space.
			A new domain is forcibly opened within the original, forming a bizarre, nested dimension.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc3:
			'''
			A tearing pain strikes your forehead. Three ghostly blue eyeballs flicker with ominous light, rolling madly beneath your skin.
			Light begins to be swallowed by this space. The abyssal whispers from within your body no longer sound like hallucinations, but distinct chewing sounds.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc4:
			'''
			Four eyes split into two pairs, covering your own eyes. The originally separate abyssal projections begin to superposition and merge.
			The world in your eyes is no longer its original shape; the structure of matter is deconstructed and reorganized within the turbid seawater.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc5:
			'''
			Your skin turns pale and swollen, like a floating corpse soaked for too long.
			Countless restless eyes swim like fish beneath your skin, fighting for space, finally converging on your forehead to tear open a hideous single eye.
			The five layers of the domain merge completely; you gain the ability to twist cause and effect within the domain.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] to restart yourself.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc6:
			'''
			The sixth eye opens upon your heart.
			What pumps is no longer warm blood, but strange black water, foul and cold, like sewage in which rotting corpses have soaked.
			Every beat stirs visible deep-blue veins within the ocean domain.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] to restart yourself.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc7:
			'''
			Seven eyes arrange themselves in a bizarre array on your forehead, bursting with light to the rhythm of time.
			The domain begins to madly erode reality; where its borders reach, matter dissolves like sand, and laws are rewritten by the tides.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] for a massive restart.
			Press [Halibut_Superposition] to use Superposition Strike.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc8:
			'''
			The eighth eye transforms into a silent vortex, appearing in the palm of your hand.
			The water pressure within the domain becomes nearly solid; light bends here, and sound is extinguished.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] for a massive restart.
			Press [Halibut_Superposition] to use Superposition Strike.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc9:
			'''
			Nine is the number of the extreme. Nine eyes form an illusory abyssal ring above your head.
			The last shred of humanity has been washed away by the seawater. What stands here now is a husk carrying an endless sea of corpses.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] for a massive restart.
			Press [Halibut_Superposition] to use Superposition Strike.
			''' */
		/* EyeDesc10:
			'''
			Layers lose their meaning; one is infinite.
			You become the Abyss, and the Abyss is you.
			Wherever your gaze falls, a new genesis begins.
			You have reached the end of this shore and become a deity of the other side.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to toggle the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the Domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] for a massive restart.
			Press [Halibut_Superposition] to use Superposition Strike.
			Hold Left Click to begin Infinite Superposition and Infinite Restart.
			''' */
		// LayerTitleFormat: Layer {0}
	}

