MuraText: {
	Subtest_Text0:
		'''
		Debemos ir al infierno para liberar el poder de la luz y la oscuridad. 
		Esto desatará una tormenta de subespacio, pero no tenemos otra opción. 
		¡Recluta, escribe un capítulo grandioso para el viaje!
		'''
	Subtest_Text1: Un enorme gusano de acero bloquea nuestro camino. Despedázalo.
	Subtest_Text2: Puedo sentir dos miradas observándonos. Ve y ocúpate de ellas.
	// World_Text0: Last Upgraded World: <{0}> | Record Level: <{1}>
	/* Subtest_Text4:
		'''
		Within the Jungle, someone's clumsy prototype still wanders. 
		As a failed experiment, it deserves to be nothing more than a heap of scrap.
		''' */
	/* Subtest_Text5:
		'''
		A shell of woven flesh, the vengeful spirits of an ancient battlefield, 
		a golem of ceaseless destruction. It destroys all, and we shall destroy it.
		''' */
	/* Subtest_Text6:
		'''
		The star god of old has long since fallen; what remains is barely a worm. 
		Let us bring a definitive end to the astral era.
		''' */
	/* Subtest_Text7:
		'''
		Let that amalgamation of spirits in the Dungeon wither beneath my edge. 
		Its souls shall serve as the finest nourishment.
		''' */
	/* Subtest_Text8:
		'''
		A pathetic god lingering on by leeching the heat of stars. 
		Her heretical flame must be thoroughly extinguished.
		''' */
	/* Subtest_Text9:
		'''
		That botanical aberration deep in the Jungle... 
		tear its petals, crush its bulb, and let its ichor stain this land.
		''' */
	/* Subtest_Text10:
		'''
		That witch who plunged into chaos has a deformed clone sister. 
		Slaughter that aberration; offer its blood and flames to the blade.
		''' */
}

